Package edu.cnm.deepdive.green_print.service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CC_APIWebService
    Uses Retrofit service to communicate with CoolClimate web service and defines classes to support of making these requests.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CC_APIWebService.GetCCAPITask
    Contains the request lifecycle for the CoolClimate web service as a BaseFluentAsyncTask subclass.
    CC_APIWebService.InstanceHolder
    Implements the initialization-on-demand holder expression for a singleton of CC_APIWebService.
    ConsumptionDBService
    Provides a service layer for accessing te ConsumptionDB Room/SQLite database.
    ConsumptionDBService.DeleteConsumptionTask
    Ability to delete items from the database
    ConsumptionDBService.InsertActivityTask
    Ability to manually insert an Activity.
    ConsumptionDBService.InsertConsumptionTask
    Implements an asynchronous INSERT of an Consumption instance into the local database.
    ConsumptionDBService.SelectAllConsumptionTask
    Implements an asynchronous SELECT of all Consumption instances (sorted in descending date order) from the local database.
    ConsumptionDBService.SelectConsumptionTask
    Provides a connection to the local database
    FragmentService
    Provides app-wide fragment management services, intended primarily for use in apps without extensive back stack requirements, where a NavigationView or BottomNavigationView is used to move between the primary UI fragments.
